      "length": 5,
      "addedAt": "2026-04-15T20:32:52.457Z"
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "content": "我想把世界上最好的都給你，卻發現世界上最好的就是你。",
      "length": 26,
      "addedAt": "2026-04-15T20:32:52.457Z"
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "content": " ",
      "length": 1,
      "addedAt": "2026-04-15T20:32:52.457Z"
    },
    {
